    "asOf": "2021-04-13",
    "date": "2021-06-21T14:47:35Z",
    "text": "G.I. and Veterans Education Empowerment Act or the GIVE Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to provide veterans and members of the Armed Forces with information about whether (1) a postsecondary education institution is listed on the College Navigator website as being affiliated with a certain religion, (2) an institution is minority serving, and (3) an institution is gender specific."
